                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" key="work_4039">al-Shawāhid fī al-ḥajar al-wāḥid</title>
                     <note>On alchemy and the philosophers stone</note>
                     <note>[If Nicollʼs conjectures as to date and autograph are right this is diff. from the work of this title ascribed to Ibn Waḥshīyah (3rd cent. A. H.) Brock. I. 243 (G1, p. 281, para. 3. no. 10, but not in Suppl.) of which the only MS. noted is Rāghib 963 (1)]</note>
                     <listBibl>
                        <bibl>Appendix Magic</bibl>
                        <bibl>[NAM. 250 (1)]</bibl>
                     </listBibl>
                     <textLang mainLang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
